WEBVTT

00:02:59.057 --> 00:03:01.793
He has this blue triangle on this chest,

00:03:03.056 --> 00:03:06.030
as all androids do,

00:03:06.744 --> 00:03:09.508
and now Vicky is in control
of this character.

00:03:09.532 --> 00:03:13.086
She can walk around, she can go anywhere,
she can look around,

00:03:13.110 --> 00:03:15.076
she can interact with her environment,

00:03:15.100 --> 00:03:17.894
and now she can tell her own stories
by making choices.

00:03:17.918 --> 00:03:20.310
So here we have our first choice.

00:03:20.334 --> 00:03:22.273
There is a fish on the ground.

00:03:22.297 --> 00:03:23.463
What should we do?

00:03:23.487 --> 00:03:25.505
Should we save it or should we leave it?

00:03:25.529 --> 00:03:27.502
Remember, we are under time pressure,

00:03:27.526 --> 00:03:28.921
so we'd better be fast.

00:03:28.945 --> 00:03:30.118
What should we do?